  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is an open-label, multicenter, extension study for subjects who completed
      NeurogesX Study C111 and received treatment with NGX-4010 (Capsaicin Patch) within 12 weeks
      (up to +7days) before entry into Study C114
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
